      • deepConvert

        public static void deepConvert(java.lang.String key,
                               java.lang.Object o,
                               TCN top)
        Converts stray arrays to TCNArray objects, recursive.
        Example:
     for (String key : tcn.map.keys()) {
         deepConvert(key, tcn.get(key), tcn);
     }
        Parameters:
        key - The key of o
        o - Any value in a TCN
        top - The TCN that o is embedded in
